    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What's your weather and cancellation policy for Austin party boats?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Weather is never your fault, so we never charge you for it. If the captain cancels for unsafe conditions, every guest gets a FREE reschedule to any future cruise, or a full refund if preferred. If weather shortens an in-progress cruise, you receive a pro-rated refund. Standard non-weather cancellations: 48-hour full-refund window after booking; after that, your deposit applies to a reschedule within 12 months. Reschedule changes 30+ days out are always free. Our refund policy is built around fairness."
